## UI Design OS (`.ai.ui/`)

**Coexistence:** [`.ai.ui/COHABITATION.md`](.ai.ui/COHABITATION.md) — UI skills write to `.work.ui/` only; do not overwrite `.work/plans/NEXT.md` except cross-links.

**Lost on UI?** [`.ai.ui/START_HERE.md`](.ai.ui/START_HERE.md) · **Router:** `@ui-process-router - <question>`

### UI completion gate (addition to Core Principle 7)

UI milestone work is not done until: UI lint/type/tests pass; `@ui-visual-verify` + `@ui-accessibility-audit` pass or are waived in `{HANDOFF_UI}`; agent-assisted UI has `@ui-concept-run - UIS-06` unless **`human-only`** in the same message.

