### UI protected files (union with existing list)

- `front-cards/app/globals.css` (token file)
- `front-cards/next.config.ts` (framework config)
- `.ai.ui/inputs/brand/` (reference — do not auto-edit)

### UI Design & implementation discipline

- No raw `#RRGGBB` or magic spacing in feature components — use `front-cards/app/globals.css` tokens.
- New primitives via `@ui-design-system add` with coverage.
- Screen work requires an **Approved** screen SPEC before `@ui-component-build start`.
- Target: WCAG AA. Focus visible; labels on controls; `prefers-reduced-motion` honored.
- Avoid generic AI chrome (gradient heroes, inconsistent radii) unless SPEC requests it.

